WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.646
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.646 --> 00:00:03.871
I'm excited to be with y'all again today.

00:00:04.093 --> 00:00:06.289
I'm going to do another 'Prayer With Me' video.

00:00:06.289 --> 00:00:08.894
I did one yesterday, and I'm going to do one today.

00:00:08.894 --> 00:00:15.260
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, I am mandating you to start doing these prayer videos more often.

00:00:15.260 --> 00:00:18.040
I need you to do these prayer videos.

00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:20.960
' And so, I'm just going to be obedient.

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:27.552
I'm sorry I haven't done more of them, and I'm going to do a lot more of them.

00:00:28.217 --> 00:00:32.590
I just want to encourage everybody today to jump in the river.

00:00:32.590 --> 00:00:43.486
You know, 'he that prayeth in an unknown tongue prayeth forth mysteries.

00:00:43.486 --> 00:00:55.440
' I believe with all my heart when you pray in the Spirit, you're praying a perfect prayer.

00:00:55.800 --> 00:01:07.479
It's coming right out of your spirit from the Holy Spirit and it's going right into the throne room.

00:01:15.392 --> 00:01:23.510
It's a coded message; in the way I believe, it's a coded message that only the Lord knows, unless He wants you to interpret it.

00:01:23.510 --> 00:01:28.413
It's not where the devil can hear.

00:01:28.413 --> 00:02:05.640
A lot of times you can be going through some trials and tribulations in your own life and you're always saying, 'Well, God, I need You to do this, I need You to do that, and I have this going on.

00:02:05.640 --> 00:02:10.900
' It's like a perfect bullseye prayer.

00:02:10.900 --> 00:02:39.164
When you're aiming at a target, you can either hit the side of it or you can hit right on the red dot every single time.

00:02:40.676 --> 00:03:01.080
I believe when you pray in the Spirit and you pray in tongues, you're hitting the bullseye every single time, praying forth mysteries and praying the heart of God.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:04.325
I really believe that.

00:03:04.325 --> 00:03:30.030
When you're praying deep prayers, you go into the rivers with the Holy Spirit and He will take you into some deep groanings sometimes, and the birthing of things you're believing for with intercessory prayer.

00:03:30.030 --> 00:03:40.840
It's like I've heard Sister Lynne Hammond talking about the doors—like going through the doors.

00:03:40.840 --> 00:04:12.093
It is exactly like that: going through the spiritual doors and opening those doors spiritually, getting our breakthrough, and getting the manifestation of what you're believing for—finances, healing, your marriage restored, your children born again and delivered from drugs.

00:04:12.093 --> 00:04:23.285
Whatever it may be, it's opening those doors in the spirit realm.

00:04:23.285 --> 00:05:13.700
People were asking me—I thought it was interesting because when you were raised like I was, and you've been praying in the Spirit since you were just a kid, a lot of people think the Christianese, the Holy Ghost, and the charismatic lingo—you know, everybody talks certain things, talking about walking and binding the devil and doing all these things.

00:05:13.700 --> 00:05:19.366
They don't understand all that.

00:05:19.366 --> 00:05:52.417
There's a lot of new faces, a lot of new Christians and new believers who are not being taught at church at all about the baptism of the Holy Spirit, how to walk in your authority, or how to take dominion and do all those things like binding and loosing.

00:05:52.417 --> 00:06:08.069
I just take it for granted because this is the way I was raised; this is what we do.

00:06:08.069 --> 00:06:27.500
If you're new to the Christian lifestyle, when you walk through the door of the church and you've never been taught, how do you know?

00:06:31.030 --> 00:06:34.457
So, I thought I would start out reading Ephesians.

00:06:34.457 --> 00:06:52.800
Read Ephesians over and over about your armor, putting on the armor, standing, and being seated with Him in the heavenlies far above all principalities.

00:06:55.777 --> 00:06:57.564
It will really bless you.

00:07:08.972 --> 00:07:09.256
I really believe that's where you could start with spiritual warfare: reading the book of Ephesians, Hebrews, and Galatians.

00:07:09.256 --> 00:07:14.195
Meditate on that word over and over again.

00:07:14.195 --> 00:07:33.549
Like it says in Ephesians, 'let the eyes of my understanding be enlightened that I may know the hope of your calling and the glorious riches of your inheritance.

00:07:33.549 --> 00:07:49.379
' Pray for the eyes of your understanding concerning the Holy Spirit, concerning Acts Chapter 2, and who we are in Christ.

00:07:49.379 --> 00:08:05.183
Pray for your eyes to be flooded with light so that you may know who you are in Christ.

00:08:23.496 --> 00:08:23.744
I would encourage you to also find old teachings from Brother Kenneth E.

00:08:23.744 --> 00:08:25.479
Hagin from Tulsa.

00:08:25.479 --> 00:08:53.976
He went home to be with the Lord in 2003—over 20 years ago—but he has amazing teachings on the authority of the believer on YouTube that will change your life.

00:08:53.976 --> 00:08:58.675
Listen to those teachings and meditate on them; just get that inside of you.

00:08:58.675 --> 00:09:10.940
Then, I have things about the blood from Sister Billy Brim about the blood covenant.

00:09:16.910 --> 00:09:17.840
I have teachings on my preaching channel, Word of Faith.

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:21.680
There's the 'Blood' from Billy Brim.

00:09:25.453 --> 00:09:40.778
Go through each one of these 'Pray with Me' videos and listen to these prayer teachings from Lynne Hammond and Lucy and meditate on what they're saying.

00:09:40.778 --> 00:09:53.290
Just get it down inside of you because it will change your life forever.

00:09:53.290 --> 00:10:04.148
Faith cometh by hearing and hearing by the word of God.

00:10:11.050 --> 00:10:16.153
It doesn't come by hearing it once; it comes by hearing it over and over again.

00:10:16.153 --> 00:10:20.690
That's how you get there.

00:10:20.690 --> 00:10:24.576
It's not just a one-time feeling.

00:10:28.231 --> 00:10:35.062
You have to be filled with the Holy Ghost because we leak.

00:10:35.062 --> 00:11:04.400
We have issues in our lives that cause us to leak out all that freshness—that fresh wine, that fresh Holy Ghost water flowing in us because of the pressures of life.

00:11:04.400 --> 00:11:16.690
When you touch a sponge, it leaks, but you have to fill it back up with water.

00:11:16.690 --> 00:11:24.465
This is what we're here today to do.

00:11:24.465 --> 00:11:31.938
Jump in the river with me and pray.

00:11:41.796 --> 00:11:42.093
I want to tell you, it's not all doom and gloom.

00:11:46.379 --> 00:11:55.702
I was asking the Lord tonight while I was doing my exercises, 'Lord, I know what You've said is coming.

00:11:55.956 --> 00:12:04.399
I know the things You've warned me about regarding the economic stuff.

00:12:04.399 --> 00:12:19.244
' When I told you all about the water and what He said, this is something that you can stop.

00:12:27.050 --> 00:12:27.353
Well, that right there gives me hope.

00:12:27.353 --> 00:12:36.310
We can stop the poisoning of the water; we can stop mass shootings.

00:12:36.310 --> 00:12:43.589
He said to go around and plead the blood of Jesus.

00:12:43.589 --> 00:12:44.980
Apply the blood.

00:12:44.980 --> 00:12:53.631
Anoint your kids with oil like I told you yesterday.

00:12:53.631 --> 00:13:00.529
Believe God for that divine protection.

00:13:06.065 --> 00:13:28.050
I told you all in a video about this time last year that we will have to have Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 deep down inside of our hearts for what's coming.

00:13:28.050 --> 00:13:46.349
You have to have a revelation of it, not just reading it once or twice a week.

00:13:54.100 --> 00:14:08.337
I'm talking about meditating on Psalm 91, muttering it, saying it out of your mouth, and getting a revelation because you will not make it in the days ahead if you do not have a spiritual foundation of the word of God inside of you.

00:14:08.337 --> 00:14:20.405
You have to make the word of God a priority in your life beyond anything else.

00:14:20.405 --> 00:14:26.290
Nothing else matters other than the word of God.

00:14:26.290 --> 00:14:39.360
I'm not talking about just playing the Bible and letting it play through without meditating on it.

00:14:39.360 --> 00:14:48.445
Pick it apart like you would a really good piece of chicken—picking it off the bone.

00:14:48.445 --> 00:14:54.853
Think about it, ponder it, and keep reading it.

00:14:54.853 --> 00:14:59.240
The word of God will change you.

00:15:02.473 --> 00:15:07.622
It should be a priority in your life, especially for what's coming.

00:15:08.378 --> 00:15:16.192
There's new revelation every morning; it never grows old.

00:15:16.192 --> 00:15:29.160
One passage of scripture will give you something totally different the next couple of days because it's ever-growing.

00:15:29.160 --> 00:15:50.180
Whenever I went to the throne room of God and stood before Him in the fear of the Lord, when He spoke, His words did not die.

00:15:50.180 --> 00:16:09.220
They became a seed right in front of me and began to grow like roots, creating a massive vine system that did not die.

00:16:09.220 --> 00:16:13.612
His words began to cultivate.

00:16:13.612 --> 00:16:27.639
If you haven't seen that video, it's a visitation in the throne room in my archives.

00:16:27.639 --> 00:16:34.982
It is absolutely amazing and will change your life.

00:16:49.185 --> 00:16:49.620
People say, 'Is America done?

00:16:49.620 --> 00:16:56.611
' I'm telling you, there's a shaking coming, but America is not done.

00:16:56.611 --> 00:17:09.023
No one knows the day or the hour of the Rapture or the end of all things.

00:17:51.190 --> 00:17:51.605
I believe we could have years or months; I just occupy until He comes.

00:17:51.605 --> 00:18:01.630
I focus on what He's told me to do.

00:18:01.630 --> 00:18:24.480
If I go by the graveside at an old age—because He said, 'With long life I will satisfy you and show you my salvation'—I believe He'll perform that.

00:18:24.480 --> 00:18:46.560
I'll do my part to take care of my body, exercise, and eat right, and He will sustain me because He has a plan for my life.

00:18:46.560 --> 00:19:31.380
Let's try our best to live long and finish strong to do what He's called us to do.

00:19:31.380 --> 00:20:12.103
Be encouraged today, but at the same time, there's a storm coming.

00:20:12.103 --> 00:20:27.948
It's a 'shaken to awaken.

00:20:27.948 --> 00:21:18.850
' It's going to be financial and many other things, but I've already told you what I saw about the beginning of this year regarding the elections going into 2025.

00:21:18.850 --> 00:21:30.992
2025 looked very dark, and I've warned you about the financial chaos.

00:21:34.738 --> 00:22:07.720
I also saw Canada, Mexico, and the United States creating a new currency—a new dollar system between the three nations—a united front to salvage what we could because of what the BRICS was doing.

00:22:18.296 --> 00:22:20.406
It wasn't as strong as before, but there was still hope.

00:22:23.789 --> 00:22:24.600
We pray for hope.

00:22:24.600 --> 00:22:31.040
People ask, 'Do you ever have a good word?

00:22:31.040 --> 00:22:32.954
' Yes!

00:22:32.954 --> 00:22:51.891
I've told you about the outpouring that's coming—a great grace explosion, a last final push for a great harvest of souls.

00:22:51.891 --> 00:23:15.644
It will happen like a mighty wave with creative miracles.

00:23:15.644 --> 00:25:20.864
But there's going to be a wake-up before there's a major revival.

00:25:20.864 --> 00:27:59.164
It'll be uncomfortable for some, but if you're part of the remnant and you're awake already, you're like the people praying on this.

00:28:21.559 --> 00:28:21.999
The Lord said, 'Don't pay attention to numbers.

00:28:21.999 --> 00:28:27.725
Do what I called you to do.

00:28:27.725 --> 00:30:34.135
Teach my people to pray.

00:30:34.135 --> 00:30:39.102
' There's blessing in obedience.

00:30:39.102 --> 00:30:47.574
I guess that's all I have right now.

00:30:47.574 --> 00:32:05.153
There's an amazing outpouring of the spirit of the Lord and it's not all doom and gloom.

00:32:05.153 --> 00:32:29.793
Very sobering days are ahead, but what do you do with sobering days?

00:32:38.027 --> 00:32:38.631
The Lord asked me, 'What's the opposite of being sober?

00:32:38.631 --> 00:32:41.887
' I said, 'Being drunk.

00:32:41.887 --> 00:32:53.430
' He said, 'Be being filled with My spirit with laughter.

00:32:53.430 --> 00:33:29.060
' If you want to make it in the days ahead, you're going to have to learn how to laugh—not just obnoxious laughing, but being filled with joy in your heart so that you don't let the drama of what we might see get on the inside of you.

00:33:47.815 --> 00:33:49.064
You have to keep showing joy because that's what people are going to be drawn to.

00:33:49.064 --> 00:34:02.311
When all heck is breaking loose, they will need someone with stability.

00:34:02.311 --> 00:34:10.166
Let Jesus shine out of you so that people see Him.

00:34:11.893 --> 00:34:33.592
The world's going to need it, and the only way we're going to do it is if you're being filled in your personal walk, getting the word, and praying.

00:34:33.592 --> 00:34:37.065
God bless you all.

00:34:37.065 --> 00:34:40.186
Let's start this prayer.

00:34:40.186 --> 00:34:49.655
Holy Spirit, we invite You into this prayer time.

00:34:49.655 --> 00:34:53.646
Have Your way.

00:34:53.646 --> 00:35:06.240
We thank You, Lord, that we are changed and going from glory to glory today.

00:35:06.240 --> 00:35:15.160
Every pore and fiber of our being shines Jesus today.

00:35:15.160 --> 00:35:23.839
Help me, Father, to be more like Jesus today.

00:35:23.839 --> 00:35:35.032
Help me to say only what You want me to say.

00:35:40.377 --> 00:35:46.254
I am yielded, filled with, and controlled by the Holy Ghost.

00:35:46.254 --> 00:35:54.280
We need a fresh drink today, Lord.

00:35:54.280 --> 00:35:56.685
We're thirsty, Jesus.

00:35:56.685 --> 00:36:00.787
won't You come and fill me?

00:36:00.787 --> 00:36:10.331
Those earthly things have left me dry; only You can satisfy.

00:36:10.331 --> 00:36:14.660
All I want is more of You.

00:36:17.733 --> 00:36:22.182
Now Lord, we just yield ourselves over to You today.

00:36:24.925 --> 00:36:31.645
You are the Potter, we are the clay; mold me and make me today.

00:36:31.645 --> 00:36:36.560
We enter boldly today into Your throne.

00:36:36.560 --> 00:36:42.050
Hey Dad, I'm here today; what's on Your heart?

00:36:58.800 --> 00:36:59.107
I don't come in as a bastard, Lord; I come in as Your son.

00:36:59.107 --> 00:37:07.380
I'm Yours, Father, and we come in boldly into that throne.

00:37:07.380 --> 00:37:19.805
We're yielded vessels to help with the warring in the spirit realm.

00:37:33.667 --> 00:37:34.454
Father, I thank You that we are yielded to You.

00:37:34.454 --> 00:37:44.840
We petition You for the things that we need.

00:37:44.840 --> 00:37:56.440
You supply all our needs according to Your riches and glory by Christ Jesus.

00:37:56.440 --> 00:38:32.048
Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:38:32.048 --> 00:38:57.311
Father, for the angels of the Lord, we send our angels out right now in the name of Jesus—from the north, south, east, and west.

00:38:57.311 --> 00:39:17.148
We call the angels to go right now in Jesus' name, bearing us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:39:17.148 --> 00:39:24.050
Get your hands off our stuff now in Jesus' name!

00:39:24.050 --> 00:39:37.480
Get your hands off our bodies now!

00:39:37.480 --> 00:39:53.928
We call for a breakthrough right now in the name of Jesus concerning our things and what we need.

00:39:53.928 --> 00:40:00.977
Out of our bellies shall flow rivers of living water.

00:40:06.245 --> 00:40:09.009
We call for the stirring of the water.

00:40:11.880 --> 00:40:18.703
We are unashamed of the Gospel of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:40:31.844 --> 00:40:35.373
We thank You, Lord, that we're not ashamed of the baptism of the Holy Ghost.

00:40:35.373 --> 00:40:37.502
We flow with You.

00:40:37.502 --> 00:40:47.712
We call for a breakthrough in the health industries and in our bodies.

00:40:47.712 --> 00:41:10.760
We call for healing, wholeness, and wellness right now from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

00:41:10.760 --> 00:41:13.738
By His stripes, we are healed.

00:41:13.738 --> 00:41:25.099
We thank You, Lord, that we don't have to be sick or broke.

00:41:40.590 --> 00:41:40.945
We have authority over the devil and tell him to get under our feet.

00:41:49.660 --> 00:41:54.055
We call ourselves healed, delivered, and well.

00:41:54.055 --> 00:42:05.715
Father, I thank You for supernatural financial breakthrough.

00:42:05.715 --> 00:42:32.674
We're not barely getting by; we have more than enough to give to the kingdom of God and those around us who need a helping hand.

00:42:32.674 --> 00:42:44.799
We're not under the curse of poverty; poverty is a curse.

00:42:51.020 --> 00:42:57.535
We call those things that be not as though they were.

00:43:12.348 --> 00:43:12.640
We thank You for creative ideas to get wealth—supernatural ideas.

00:43:12.640 --> 00:43:44.220
We will be the head and not the tail.

00:43:44.220 --> 00:44:05.027
There's a supernatural turnaround right now in the name of Jesus.

00:44:32.071 --> 00:44:32.635
We call forth marriages to be restored right now.

00:44:32.635 --> 00:44:56.369
Where they say there is no hope, You are the hope.

00:44:56.369 --> 00:45:22.549
We bind the devil off of marriages.

00:45:58.840 --> 00:45:59.800
We pray over the children; there is no rebellion in them.

00:45:59.800 --> 00:47:56.875
Father, You said in Your word to spare the rod and spoil the child—that there would be leadership to train a child up in the way they should go.

00:48:08.920 --> 00:48:37.200
We thank You for bringing the children home.

00:48:37.200 --> 00:49:21.830
There's a move of God in the youth—a supernatural outpouring of Your Spirit upon the young children.

00:49:22.435 --> 00:49:50.599
We thank You for visitations and manifestations of Your glory even on the youth.

00:49:50.599 --> 00:50:12.555
Somebody's being healed of cancer right now.

00:52:22.290 --> 00:52:22.827
I see an elderly person; I call in full manifestation of Your healing power over them.

00:52:22.827 --> 00:52:43.415
We pray over thyroids.

00:53:01.799 --> 00:53:15.580
I command Hashimoto's to be gone right now.

00:53:15.580 --> 00:54:08.799
Any nodules, we curse the nodules and command them to go.

00:54:08.799 --> 00:54:48.160
I call for hormones to be completely healed and whole.

00:55:29.220 --> 00:55:29.920
I speak to ears to open.

00:55:36.662 --> 00:56:06.640
I call the hair fibers inside of the ear healed and whole from tinnitus.

00:56:06.640 --> 00:56:47.298
No more ringing in the ears, no more deaf ears.

00:56:47.298 --> 00:57:29.309
Even in the retinas, I call the eyes to be healed.

00:57:29.319 --> 00:57:50.349
New irises, new nerve endings.

00:58:23.320 --> 00:58:24.219
I call those detached eyes healed from demonic attack or accidents.

00:59:25.180 --> 00:59:26.640
The Lord just showed me backs—I call backs healed from all the vertebrae and discs.

00:59:47.329 --> 00:59:51.059
I call for restoration over those backs, all the way to the tailbone.

00:59:51.059 --> 01:00:03.743
Dislocated ribs, we call them healed and whole.

01:00:03.743 --> 01:00:15.929
Over legs, hips, and knees—we call the joints to be whole.

01:00:33.115 --> 01:00:33.470
I see brain issues—actually, a stroke.

01:00:51.048 --> 01:00:51.816
We call strokes healed in Jesus' name.

01:00:51.816 --> 01:01:09.490
Paralyzed faces, we call them healed.

01:01:09.490 --> 01:01:16.360
Blood clots, healed.

01:01:32.438 --> 01:02:09.281
We thank You, Lord, that You're the restorer of memory and the pathways of the blood through the brain.

01:02:40.445 --> 01:02:40.994
Open the eyes of my heart, Lord.

01:02:44.859 --> 01:02:59.079
I want to see You high and lifted up, shining in the light of Your glory.

01:02:59.079 --> 01:03:11.719
Pour out Your power and love as we sing, 'Holy, holy, holy.

01:03:11.719 --> 01:03:14.649
' I want to see You.

01:03:21.107 --> 01:03:21.820
You inhabit the praises of Your people.

01:03:21.820 --> 01:03:31.360
When praises go up, blessings come down.

01:03:31.360 --> 01:03:36.819
We exalt Thee, oh Lord.

01:03:41.125 --> 01:03:42.553
You are high above all the earth.

01:03:42.553 --> 01:03:50.888
We magnify, glorify, and adore You.

01:03:57.093 --> 01:03:57.906
The glory is here.

01:03:57.906 --> 01:04:08.159
Oh Lord, You're beautiful; Your face is all I see.

01:04:08.159 --> 01:04:20.728
And when Your eyes are on this child, Your grace abounds to me.

01:04:20.728 --> 01:04:25.089
Jesus, what a wonder You are.

01:04:25.089 --> 01:04:32.555
You're the sweetest name of all.

01:04:54.009 --> 01:04:54.975
You always hear me when I call.

01:05:00.720 --> 01:05:02.804
You lift me up each time I fall.

01:05:02.804 --> 01:05:43.057
Your name is like honey on my lips, Your spirit's like water to my soul, Your word is a lamp unto my feet.

01:05:43.057 --> 01:05:44.720
Jesus, I love You.

01:05:44.720 --> 01:06:01.210
My daughter Megan feels the presence of the Lord.

01:06:01.210 --> 01:06:17.119
She overcomes special needs, but when the presence of the Lord comes in, she gets giggly.

01:06:17.119 --> 01:06:21.299
This was a refreshing for those watching.

01:06:21.299 --> 01:06:27.090
If you're dry, just drink.

01:06:27.090 --> 01:06:29.894
Bread of Heaven, feed us until we want no more.

01:06:29.894 --> 01:06:48.920
This is where the seeing comes—when you enter in like this, He starts showing you things.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
I've had eight visitations from Jesus face to face, and it comes out of this intimacy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
It doesn't come out of begging; it comes out of relationship and worship.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Build an intimacy with the Father.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
I'm nothing special; I'm just a servant who has been sent to help you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I say 'filled with what?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
'—His glory.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I hope this video blessed you today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart because Jesus loves you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Great days are ahead for the remnant.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
God bless you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Shalom, shalom.
